Do I need authentication?
No, authentication is not required. It's optional if you wish to demonstrate it. If you do implement
it, keep it simple (e.g., using a hardcoded user or token).
How polished should the submission be?
Your submission should run cleanly, feature readable code, and demonstrate basic validation
and error handling.
What if I run out of time?
That’s fine. Just note what’s missing, what you’d do next, and any assumptions in your
README.